ek.","pos":[3435,3475]},{"content":"If a worker has eight hours of sick time, the difference of 32 hours can be calculated automatically.","pos":[3476,3577]},{"content":"Workers' compensation","pos":[3610,3631]},{"content":"Click <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Add<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept>, and select a compensation state and a compensation code.","pos":[3641,3725],"source":"Click <strong>Add</strong>, and select a compensation state and a compensation code."},{"content":"Repeat these steps for any additional workers' compensation benefits.","pos":[3726,3795]},{"content":"Earnings","pos":[3829,3837]},{"content":"The fields in this group interact in the following ways to determine how earnings are generated and shown on earnings statements:","pos":[3847,3976],"source":"The fields in this group interact in the following ways to determine how earnings are generated and shown on earnings statements:\n"},{"content":"If neither <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Generate salary<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> nor <bpt id=\"p2\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Generate earnings from schedule<ept id=\"p2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> is selected, base earnings statement lines for the position aren't generated.","pos":[3986,4160],"source":"If neither <strong>Generate salary</strong> nor <strong>Generate earnings from schedule</strong> is selected, base earnings statement lines for the position aren't generated."},{"content":"Only the recurring earnings that are specified on the <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Worker<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> page are generated.","pos":[4161,4258],"source":" Only the recurring earnings that are specified on the <strong>Worker</strong> page are generated."},{"content":"If <bpt id=\"p1\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Generate earnings from schedule<ept id=\"p1\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> is selected, but <bpt id=\"p2\">&lt;strong&gt;</bpt>Generate salary<ept id=\"p2\">&lt;/strong&gt;</ept> isn't selected, the following information applies:","pos